.section
	h1 Site Information
	p Add site information to your organization here. Information that will be shown on the mobile app is mark with **
.section
	h2 Select your colors
	row.color-control
		.col-md-9
			input.form-control.title-value(ng-model="sites[selectedSite].tittle1" name="title1" type="text" placeholder="Site Tittle **" required )
		.col-md-3
			input.form-control.color-picker(ng-model="sites[selectedSite].colorTitle1" name="tittle2" type="text" placeholder="Main Color" required)
	.row.color-control
		.col-md-9
			input.form-control.title-value(ng-model="sites[selectedSite].tittle2" name="title1" type="text" placeholder="Site Tittle **" required )
		.col-md-3
			input.form-control.color-picker(ng-model="sites[selectedSite].colorTitle2" name="tittle2" type="text" placeholder="Border Color" required)
.section
	h2 About your bussines
	p Our customer want to know more about you!! Scroll throw and answer the following questions.
.section
	h2 Search Criteria
	p This information could be useful to others for found your information
	row
		.search-criteria-control
			.search-body
				div(slimscroll="" slimscroll-option="{height:'auto'}")
					.col-md-1.tag(ng-repeat="tag in sites[selectedSite].searchTags")
						.btn-close(ng-click="removeSiteTag($index)")
							span X
						p {{tag}}
			.search-add
				.col-md-9
					input.form-control(ng-model="newTagField")
				.col-md-3
					button.btn.btn-default(ng-click="addSiteTag(newTagField);newTagField=''") Add